    {
      "id": "X6sujFQMaGGYq93pK2Edo",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 47.10163857821749,
      "y": 3415.722306478048,
      "width": 1397,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 409916532,
      "version": 124,
      "versionNonce": 2143296204,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783681727731,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Idea: Do not update followers' timelines when a tweet is posted. Instead, fetch tweets when the follower opens their Home page.\n\nThis is for Celebraties\n\nFlow:\n    Ronaldo tweets\n      │\n      ▼\n    Tweet DB\n\n    (No timeline updates)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Idea: Do not update followers' timelines when a tweet is posted. Instead, fetch tweets when the follower opens their Home page.\n\nThis is for Celebraties\n\nFlow:\n    Ronaldo tweets\n      │\n      ▼\n    Tweet DB\n\n    (No timeline updates)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "TDE01NHDaamrmcRUbEGPH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 69.93389442227908,
      "y": 3750.044729707121,
      "width": 460.1178283691406,
      "height": 387.9159807145462,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1k",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2105346380,
      "version": 132,
      "versionNonce": 822796620,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783681727731,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Later...\n\n    Alice opens Home\n      │\n    Read Alice Timeline\n      │\n    Find celebrity accounts Alice follows\n      │\n    Fetch their latest tweets\n      │\n    Merge results\n      │\n    Return Home Feed",
      "fontSize": 23.87175265935669,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Later...\n\n    Alice opens Home\n      │\n    Read Alice Timeline\n      │\n    Find celebrity accounts Alice follows\n      │\n    Fetch their latest tweets\n      │\n    Merge results\n      │\n    Return Home Feed",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "U4oaWpYzrQxdUX8A2so06",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 141.26766447615495,
      "y": 4205.144017087161,
      "width": 633.1416551784687,
      "height": 185.4274190202819,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1l",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 116432972,
      "version": 311,
      "versionNonce": 708368332,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783681727731,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Timeline DB\n    Alice Timeline\n        Bob Tweet 101\n        Charlie Tweet 205\nNotice that Ronaldo's tweets are NOT stored here.\n\nThey are fetched dynamically during read.",
      "fontSize": 21.19170503088936,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Timeline DB\n    Alice Timeline\n        Bob Tweet 101\n        Charlie Tweet 205\nNotice that Ronaldo's tweets are NOT stored here.\n\nThey are fetched dynamically during read.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "IubwmiYA5k3YIdt5nRGlH",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1612.520537368665,
      "y": 4683.087625825476,
      "width": 431.34737795549756,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1n",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1531572172,
      "version": 69,
      "versionNonce": 893809228,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783681747848,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Twitter combines both approaches.\n\nNormal Users\n        │\nFan-out-on-Write (Push)\n        │\nTimeline DB\n\n\nCelebrity Users\n        │\nFan-out-on-Read (Pull)\n        │\nFetch during timeline request",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Twitter combines both approaches.\n\nNormal Users\n        │\nFan-out-on-Write (Push)\n        │\nTimeline DB\n\n\nCelebrity Users\n        │\nFan-out-on-Read (Pull)\n        │\nFetch during timeline request",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4fRLxunnXK0KGqQ3N7VIS",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1695.456355516772,
      "y": 4567.446718412824,
      "width": 865.872238740401,
      "height": 100.83390497600516,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1o",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 899862348,
      "version": 189,
      "versionNonce": 859898188,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783681750564,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Hybrid Approach (Used by Twitter)\n",
      "fontSize": 43.840828250437035,
      "fontFamily": 7,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Hybrid Approach (Used by Twitter)\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.15
    },
    {
      "id": "NHb4iXl_k_8MFdNdCiP0v",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -1592.917668614554,
      "y": 5135.451194622265,
      "width": 242,
      "height": 350,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1p",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1784148300,
      "version": 64,
      "versionNonce": 584730828,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783681747848,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "When Alice opens Home:\n\nTimeline DB\n(Bob, Charlie Tweets)\n          +\nCelebrity Tweets\n(Ronaldo)\n          +\nAds\n          +\nRecommendations\n          │\n          ▼\nFinal Home Timeline",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "When Alice opens Home:\n\nTimeline DB\n(Bob, Charlie Tweets)\n          +\nCelebrity Tweets\n(Ronaldo)\n          +\nAds\n          +\nRecommendations\n          │\n          ▼\nFinal Home Timeline",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "VT7usmR0pE1AFBXp4USTs",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -902.294865607636,
      "y": 4764.034905053785,
      "width": 2440.989081817998,
      "height": 414.705550612621,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
